sequenceDiagram
actor Scheduler
participant PredictiveService
participant DataLake
participant MLFramework
participant AlertingSystem
Scheduler->>PredictiveService: Trigger Prediction Job
PredictiveService->>DataLake: Fetch Data
DataLake->>PredictiveService: Return Data
PredictiveService->>MLFramework: Execute Model
MLFramework->>PredictiveService: Return Prediction
PredictiveService->>AlertingSystem: Send Alert (if threshold exceeded)